# Backtest data is each user's OWN — built locally from Kalshi market data as
# their bot runs. Never ship it: keeps downloads clean, avoids merge conflicts on
# pull, and means nobody inherits anyone else's data. (backtest_data/README.md is
# kept; only the live .json data is ignored.)
backtest_data/*.json
